{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Compulsory minimum wage for class 1 HGV drivers of \u00a318 per hour",
        "additional_details": "We think a minimum wage of \u00a318 per hour would better reflect the pressure and stress HGV drivers are under.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to set minimum wage of \u00a318 per hour for HGV class 1 drivers, due to the high risks these drivers are exposed to and the risk of fines. We also believe it would improve safety of others on the road. ",
